{
    "body": "<p>Ghouls are cunning and versatile enemies, and can be used in many scenarios for an undead-focused campaign.</p>", 
    "name": "Encounters", 
    "url": "pfsrd://Monster Codex/Rules/Ghouls/Encounters", 
    "type": "section", 
    "source": "Monster Codex", 
    "sections": [
        {
            "body": "<p>These stealthy serial killers might live near the edge of a village or large city and terrorize the locals by breaking in and slaughtering entire families. After a few weeks of terror, they move on to another village and start the carnage anew.</p>", 
            "name": "Second-Story Killers", 
            "url": "pfsrd://Monster Codex/Rules/Ghouls/Encounters/Second-Story Killers", 
            "type": "section", 
            "source": "Monster Codex", 
            "abbrev": "CR 5", 
            "sections": [
                {
                    "body": "<p class='stat-block-1'><b>CR </b>CR 3</p><p class='stat-block-1'><b>XP </b>800</p><p class='stat-block-1'><b>hp </b>37</p>", 
                    "url": "pfsrd://Monster Codex/Rules/Ghouls/Encounters/Second-Story Killers/Ghoul Creeper", 
                    "type": "section", 
                    "name": "Ghoul Creeper", 
                    "source": "Monster Codex"
                }, 
                {
                    "body": "<p class='stat-block-1'><b>CR </b>CR 1</p><p class='stat-block-1'><b>XP </b>400 each</p><p class='stat-block-1'><b>hp </b>13 each</p>", 
                    "name": "Ghouls", 
                    "url": "pfsrd://Monster Codex/Rules/Ghouls/Encounters/Second-Story Killers/Ghouls", 
                    "source": "Monster Codex", 
                    "abbrev": "2", 
                    "type": "section"
                }
            ]
        }, 
        {
            "body": "<p>This hunting party could be searching for someone in particular, or might just be out trying to fill the larders. A hunting party might attack a small caravan near a less traveled road or even a small village.</p>", 
            "name": "Ghoul Hunting Party", 
            "url": "pfsrd://Monster Codex/Rules/Ghouls/Encounters/Ghoul Hunting Party", 
            "type": "section", 
            "source": "Monster Codex", 
            "abbrev": "CR 10", 
            "sections": [
                {
                    "body": "<p class='stat-block-1'><b>CR </b>CR &mdash</p><p class='stat-block-1'><b>XP </b>&mdash</p><p class='stat-block-1'><b>hp </b>16</p>", 
                    "url": "pfsrd://Monster Codex/Rules/Ghouls/Encounters/Ghoul Hunting Party/Corpse Cat", 
                    "type": "section", 
                    "name": "Corpse Cat", 
