                    "type": "section", 
                    "name": "Masked Murderer", 
                    "source": "Monster Codex"
                }
            ]
        }, 
        {
            "body": "<p>This pair of ghoul spellcasters and their bodyguards are much more than casual thugs. They are likely to be at the heart of a larger plot or traveling to secure a source of fresh meat for themselves and their kin. This encounter works well following the ghoul hunting party detailed above.</p>", 
            "name": "Grave Trouble", 
